{"tid":2247542,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：日本尖閣諸島問題容易牽動國內戰狼情緒 應以靜悄悄外交方式解決","createTime":"2020-10-18T02:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T03:45:53.000Z","uid":21470,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e9001f6ce7b6524ea8d0a3e8556fe05752e6db","tid":2247542,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T02:42:20.000Z","msg":"駐日華使指暫無考慮把釣魚島問題訴諸國際法院<br />\n<br />\n中國駐日大使孔鉉佑表示，中方暫時沒有考慮將釣魚島問題訴諸國際法院，強調中方願意同日方通過對話協商，尋求妥善解決辦法。孔鉉佑接受日本富士電視台訪問，說釣魚島問題事關領土主權，牽動中日國民感情，十分複雜敏感，應通過外交等渠道，<span class=\"gold\">以靜悄悄的方式</span>開展溝通，又強調釣魚島及附屬島嶼是中國固有領土，必須在嚴格遵循過往共識的基礎上，找到雙方都能接受的解決辦法。<br />\n<br />\n孔鉉佑又表示，抗疫和盡快恢復經濟，仍是中日兩國頭等大事，在疫情告一段落後，中日會就國家主席習近平國事訪問日本的時機和安排等溝通協調，強調雙方都認為必須確保在最適宜的時機、環境和氛圍下實現訪問，會透過各層級對話溝通做好充分準備，為兩國高層往來營造積極氣氛和良好條件。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2362116\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2362116&d=lXXpVpUBFe4etFVyslLGPTC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=144e3fce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2362116</a>"},{"pid":"4fe365f30d12f09d25b60c6d9a4760a7b2b8f2fb","tid":2247542,"uid":61280,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T02:43:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">&quot;中央咁做係用心良苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！&quot;</span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3659e67942d31e008762452fa9cf31c90743f57b","tid":2247542,"uid":183758,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T02:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ggwqZ4o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FggwqZ4o.gif&h=1da21c7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ji4PHhK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJi4PHhK.png&h=437b2b16&s={SIZE}\"